        protected int doProbability(Evu evu)
        Description copied from class: Process
        Gets the appropriate process next state probability from the VegetativeType associated with the Evu in the parameter. This is the default doProbability method which subclasses end up calling if they don't implement their own method.
        Overrides:

        Parameters:
        evu - is an Evu.
        Returns:
        an int, the process probability

      • isRegenDelayCommon

        private static boolean isRegenDelayCommon(RegionalZone zone,
                         Evu evu)
        computes common regeneration delay for an evu in a zone.
        Parameters:
        zone -
        evu -
        Returns:
        false if not in regeneration delay or no species found.

        True if habitat type group is A1, A2, B2, D3, or E2 AND species = NS Mesic Shrubs, Upland Grasses, Xeric Shrubs, Alpine or Altered Grasses or Native vorbs AND the evu succession is not 3 decades

      • regenNew

        private static VegetativeType regenNew(RegionalZone zone,
                      Evu evu,
                      Lifeform lifeform,
                      Lifeform regenLifeform)
        The Adjacent Process we are looking at below and in the other R1 regen could be either the process at the begin or end of the current time step, depending on whether or not its doNextState function has been called yet. He decided that this gives the a bit of variability and its perhaps a good thing. Also discussed the idea of ordering the seed species first by lifeform type than by acres within lifeforms, with Trees being first.
        Parameters:
        zone -
        evu -
        Returns:

      • regenCommon

        private static VegetativeType regenCommon(RegionalZone zone,
                         Evu evu)
        Build a hashtable: key = species, value = acres; if species is seed producing add its acres to the value already in the hashtable. Special note: When two units of equal acres provide seed source, there is no code the distinguishes them, the species chosen is strictly dependent on the ordering of adjacent units.
        Parameters:
        zone -
        evu -
        Returns:
